snippet.textDisplay:
I've been sexually assaulted and if that person were to make a video like this (I'm not saying all experiences are the same; all trauma is unique) then I would feel nothing and no personal healing would come from it. The only healing that could come out of this is for future situations. Situations like this, where such awareness is raised, can allow people the opportunity to educate themselves more about consent and SA/SH/R.
Peace and love to all survivors; you are all beautiful and deserving of love. <3
